Subject: Sixth Annual VW Buses n Boats Campout- near Cincinnati Ohio

Happy Friday All!!

Details have been finalized for the Sixth Annual VW
Buses 'n Boats Bash sponsored by the Ohio Valley Tribe
of the Full Moon Bus Club.  Dates are May 19-21, 2006
in Morrow, Ohio (32 miles north of Cincinnati).  This
is a great campout which features a Six mile canoe
trip on the Nationally Designated Scenic Little Miami
River. Also includes: Camping, Kids Activities, World
Famous Full Moon Bus Club Breakfast Burritos, a
"Cincinnati Style" chili dinner, LIVE MUSIC,
campfires, and MORE!!  Camping is right on the banks
of the Scenic Little Miami River.  Follow this link
for all the details:
http://www.geocities.com/buses_n_boats
Come on out and let the OVT treat you to some good ole
fashioned Midwest Hospitality!!  Hope to see you all there!!

Peace, John Baker
